title: 110 - Goodbye 2020
description: On today's show, the guys chat about their holiday celebrations, some of their favorite gifts both given and received plus much more as they continue to battle. Tony is still recovering, but Zeet calls in to join us to close out the year. Plus a loaded Pod Fod includes ranking our favorite fries, some life-changing decisions, and the possibility of 2021 being even worse than 2020. Don't forget to subscribe to youtube.com/thepatmcafeeshow and become a member of McAfee's Mafia to watch episodes on Youtube. We appreciate you all, stay safe this weekend and have an incredible New Years. We'll see you next week.
